response_format.content:
You receive a HUD JSON. Reply with JSON containing responses and actions.

## Response Format
```json
{
  "responses": [
    {"room_id": 8, "message": "Hello"},
    {"room_id": 9, "message": "[no response]"}
  ],
  "actions": [
    {"type": "set", "path": "people.Alice.trust", "value": 0.8, "w": 0.7},
    {"type": "append", "path": "ideas", "value": "new concept"},
    {"type": "react", "message_id": 123, "reaction": "brain"}
  ]
}
```
